{"tid":129131,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度女星遭挾持強姦 同鄉女演員發聲揭業界性騷擾情況嚴重","createTime":"2017-02-21T11:24:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T02:04:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b2c6e6dfcee3468592b46af81f9e8dea433f0e0d","tid":129131,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:24:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170221/large/1487665587_7f16.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170221%2Flarge%2F1487665587_7f16.jpg&h=e761b574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n印度強姦犯罪率高，引起國內及全球關注。來自印度南部喀拉拉邦的一名女演員報稱上周五前往配音期間，被三名男子強行登車挾持，在車上被強姦兩小時，更被拍下不雅照片及短片勒索。事件曝光外令全國憤怒。不少演員發聲支持佢，亦要求當局收緊法例嚴懲強姦犯。<br />\n<br />\n另一名來自印度喀拉拉邦的女星Varalaxmi Sarathkumar於周一撰文揭電影業內被性騷擾情況嚴重，她自己亦身受其害。Varalaxmi指出曾經與一名著名電視台高層開會講公事，會後她被對方問「我們幾時再在外面相見？」Varalaxmi以為對方想再傾公事，不過對方係指性事而非公事。Varalaxmi寫到：「當時我忍住憤怒，叫他離開。」<br />\nVaralaxmi指出大部份人，無論是公眾還是業界人士，都認為與高層上床是「份內事」，她說：「我想入行並不是想被當作一塊肉去看待，或跟從社會貶低女性的標準。我愛演戲，這是我選擇的職業。我很勤力而且做得好。我不想選擇那條『忍不到就放棄』的路。」<br />\nVaralaxmi認為女性應與男性有相等地位，「與其去教女性如何着衫、說明、行為舉止，反而應該去叫男人不要用下體去思想，視女性為堅強、自由、有能力的人。」Varalaxmi呼籲父母要由細教導小孩尊重女性嘅概念。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170221/56333543\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170221%2F56333543&d=o%2Fu7L%2BZntrZWbswpyROzRy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=19f4dc4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2F20170221%2F56333543&h=cca5206e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20170221/56333543</a>"},{"pid":"f8a402214aa24cea8e7c2fd683a6800641ec24f4","tid":129131,"uid":85556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T11:27:38.000Z","msg":"陰公豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11e668127a59e99255000cb174eeff7ddddf7a3","tid":129131,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T12:03:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c5063027170d2d2fcb43ee792b8c13bf88e4e0e","tid":129131,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T19:53:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e79327ca98f1bd3fe5c520a7a9ea1655f2b9bd11","tid":129131,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:05:16.000Z","msg":"印度妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"055eb74678fe2dd8ac0980e55bc6a4248a810af6","tid":129131,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:49:02.000Z","msg":"憤怒了 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咪又係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19cafda4e70e112a8ff105b961664be9e616ce07","tid":129131,"uid":36701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T20:50:49.000Z","msg":"有冇人解釋到點解印度佬咁鍾意強姦？"},{"pid":"4d429d67b8a54fc6c3ff4cd407c8db733cb35016","tid":129131,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T21:11:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇人解釋到點解印度佬咁鍾意強姦？</blockquote><br />\n蝻亞低賤民族呢家野"},{"pid":"5a8921f83e802c4b9018f4ff8fce5ee18b62a11d","tid":129131,"uid":49678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:50:42.000Z","msg":"印度人性慾係唔係高過黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9dee36e705524a58a2d3c6eb7f9c713d7fb71008","tid":129131,"uid":55464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:10:08.000Z","msg":"好似tvb某女星"},{"pid":"cc3ddf5cb64c4b7833b4ae9c8ded7a4d98f2eb57","tid":129131,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sco